  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>Humidifiers discharge a highly salinated mist from the rocket nozzles, conducting a dramatic streak of electricity during Jetpack operation.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>加湿器会在火箭喷口释放高盐分水雾，使得喷气背包在飞行期间将留下一道绚丽的电气尾迹。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>加濕器從火箭噴嘴釋放出高鹽化霧氣，在噴射背包運轉時引導強烈電流。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
